snippet.title: Barbie Fashion Show - an eye for style - PC Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Barbie has just won Fashion Designer of the Year and her new success as a fashion designer has filled her design studio with orders! Join Barbie and Teresa as they design new outfits for all kinds of customers. With more customization options than ever, your fashions are sure to be a huge hit.

The studio is where it all happens! Once you receive your first customer order, you’ll be ready to design new outfits. The orders start out simple and get bigger as you complete each show. But, you’ll get lots of new fabrics, accessories, and runway items to help you along the way.

Barbie Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sYZ2bGcITQ&list=PLs4m9NHR3dBDg9DpamuMVJTapNhYlxdmh
